Package: nfda
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Functional Data Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-10-20
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Mueller", 
                  email = "smuller@data-zoo.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Simon Mueller <smuller@data-zoo.de>
Description: Nonparametric methods for functional data analysis including 
    kernel regression and classification. Implements methods based on 
    semimetrics (PCA, derivatives, PLS) with various bandwidth selection 
    techniques. Originally based on methods by Ferraty and Vieu.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
